        <scopecontent id="ref1">
            <head>Scope and Content of Collection</head>
            <p>Digital interview recordings of Japanese Americans relating to immigration to the United States from Japan, internment of Japanese Americans during World War II, and the post-war Japanese American community. Interviews conducted by Kaoru Ueda. Includes images of diaries, newsletters, and other textual material.</p>
        </scopecontent>
