                </bioghist>
                <scopecontent id="ref40">
                    <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
                    <p>Kurotaki discusses how to maintain the temple as a traditional religious place for Issei and Japanese expats and to find solutions to evolve as the Japanese American community changes.</p>
